        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8280",
        "content": "\"Ah ha! um h'm! suppose you give us the benefit of it,\" suggested Lilburn good naturally, \"I'm open to conviction.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
