        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8280",
        "content": "That fellow Nick Ward, is a noted blackleg and ruffian: had his nose broken in a fight and is sensitive on the subject; was cheating of course.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
